name: Mi&Miau Pink/Blue
description:
This charming porcelain salt and pepper set is disguised in blue cat outfit and pink bear outfit. The exceptional quality figurines are made from the finest white porcelain and are hand painted.

Dimensions: 11cm high approx.

Designed by StMilo
Made in Herend
